Description: cd2030.core is an R package for managing and validating data formatted 
    according to Countdown 2030 standards. It provides tools for data loading,
    cleaning, and validation, detecting issues like missing values, inconsistencies, 
    outliers, and ratio anomalies. The package ensures compliance with Countdown 2030 
    guidelines and generates standardized data quality reports, enabling users to 
    focus on analysis and interpretation.
